# Keep the build context small and the build reproducible.
# `**/target/` (not just `target/`) so nested build dirs are excluded too — e.g.
# the fuzz crate's own workspace at libs/1-sources/1-postgres/fuzz/target/ (~1GB).
**/target/
.git/
.github/
**/*.md
# …but 14 crates embed their README at compile time via
# `#![doc = include_str!("../README.md")]`, so the build needs them present.
# This negation MUST stay after the broad `**/*.md` ignore to win.
!**/README.md
dev/grafana/
dev/prometheus/
docker-compose*.yml
Dockerfile
.dockerignore
